thread.title: Karen Scott
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Karen Scott

author: Karen Scott
title: Karen Scott
text: This was my first time ordering non-Canon ink, so was a little apprehensive, but there are so many good reviews of Ink Station that I thought I'd give it a go. The ink arrived the following day, just in time as I needed two cartridges next time I went to print a document. Perfect! This will be where I'll be ordering all my ink in future.
